      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering peak torque through individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension utilizes OEM-spec Bilstein dampers for precise damping and rebound. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical synchromesh and compression across all cylinders are excellent.",
